HEADWORD: Sworder
<hw>Sword"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who uses, or
fights with, a sword; a swordsman; a soldier; a cutthroat.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

